Here is the code for a simple landing page for a car dealership:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Car Dealership</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Inventory</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="banner">
            <img src="car-image.jpg" alt="Car Image">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Car Dealership</h1>
            <p>Find your dream car today!</p>
            <button>Explore Our Inventory</button>
        </section>
        <section class="features">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Wide selection of cars</li>
                <li>Competitive pricing</li>
                <li>Excellent customer service</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="call-to-action">
            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
            <p>Visit us today or contact us to learn more about our cars.</p>
            <button>Contact Us</button>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Car Dealership</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

And here is the CSS code in a separate file called `styles.css`:
```css
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

header {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 1em;
    text-align: center;
}

header nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
}

header nav ul li {
    margin-right: 20px;
}

header nav a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.banner {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #333, #666);
    background-size: 100% 300px;
    background-position: 0% 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color: #fff;
}

.banner img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    z-index: -1;
}

.features {
    padding: 2em;
}

.features ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

.features li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.call-to-action {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 2em;
    text-align: center;
}

.call-to-action button {
    background-color: #666;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 1em;
    text-align: center;
    clear: both;
}
```
Please note that you will need to replace the `car-image.jpg` with your own image. Also, this is just a basic template and you may need to add more styles and functionality to make it fully functional.

